    "document": "Function: riscv_nn_conv_HWC_u8_s8_s8_sym_bias_fast\nSummary: Replaced ENA_TILING GEMM with im2col + 4x4 vd4dotsu GEMM (nn_mat_mul_kernel_u8_q7_bias_2sft_unroll4) \u2014 4.00x speedup\nApproach: Same pattern as s8_s8_s8 and u8_u8_s8 variants. Replaced weight transpose + tiling GEMM (vectorize col2=32, 12.5% VL util) with 4-pixel im2col + nn_mat_mul_kernel_u8_q7_bias_2sft_unroll4 (4x4 vd4dotsu, vectorize K). No new kernel needed \u2014 reused existing unroll4.\nCycles before: 2292583\nCycles after: 573699\nSpeedup: 4.00x\nPipeline insight: Assembly: 8 vle8 + 16 vd4dotsu per inner loop iter (M1). Same structure as u8_u8_s8 kernel at parity.\nLesson: u8_s8_s8 variant mechanically follows the same tiling GEMM \u2192 im2col + unroll4 pattern. nn_mat_mul_kernel_u8_q7_bias_2sft_unroll4 already existed \u2014 just needed to wire it up. Expect same ~4x for all remaining sym_bias_fast and sym_fast type variants.\nOutcome: improved\nTags: conv, sym, GEMM, 4x4-tiling, vd4dotsu, u8_s8",
